OL,3,CWill John Lewis pay staff an annual
OL,4,Cbonus for first time in four years?
OL,6,FWorkers at the John Lewis Partnership
OL,7,Fare set to find out whether they will
OL,8,Freceive their first annual bonus
OL,9,Fpayment in four years next week.
OL,11,FThe retail group, which runs the John
OL,12,FLewis department store chain and
OL,13,FWaitrose supermarket business, will
OL,14,Falso reveal how it has been
OL,15,Fprogressing with its transformation
OL,16,Fstrategy in an update on Thursday
OL,17,FMarch 12.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
