OL,3,CWill John Lewis pay staff an annual
OL,4,Cbonus for first time in four years?
OL,6,FIt will report its results for the
OL,7,Fyear to January, which will include
OL,8,Finforming staff over its plans for any
OL,9,Fpotential bonus.
OL,11,FIt is still not clear whether the
OL,12,Femployee-owned business will pay an
OL,13,Fannual bonus to its staff, who the
OL,14,Fretail group call partners.
OL,16,FThe payment of a bonus is decided by
OL,17,Fthe company's board.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
