OL,3,CWill John Lewis pay staff an annual
OL,4,Cbonus for first time in four years?
OL,6,FJLP has not paid an annual bonus to
OL,7,Fworkers since January 2022 amid a
OL,8,Fmajor turnaround strategy at the
OL,9,Fcompany.
OL,11,FFollowing the coronavirus pandemic,
OL,12,Fthe group shut a number of John Lewis
OL,13,Fdepartment stores and cut head office
OL,14,Fjobs in a bid to shore up its finances.
OL,16,FLast year, the company opted not to
OL,17,Fhand out a bonus again despite seeing
OL,18,Fannual profits triple.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
