PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773052871
OL,3,CWill John Lewis pay staff an annual
OL,4,Cbonus for first time in four years?
OL,6,FJLP saw underlying profits rebound
OL,7,Fhigher to #126 million for the year to
OL,8,FJanuary last year, from #42 million a
OL,9,Fyear earlier.
OL,11,FLast summer, the company indicated in
OL,12,Fan internal update that staff could be
OL,13,Fin line for a bonus if it beats a #200
OL,14,Fmillion profit target.
OL,16,FAt its peak during the 1980s, the
OL,17,Fretailer paid an annual bonus worth as
OL,18,Fmuch as 24% of employee salaries.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
