PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773052871
OL,3,CWill John Lewis pay staff an annual
OL,4,Cbonus for first time in four years?
OL,6,FAfter it was not paid out for a third
OL,7,Fconsecutive year, a number of
OL,8,Ffrustrated workers signed an open
OL,9,Fletter calling on bosses to bring the
OL,10,Fbonus back.
OL,12,FLast month, JLP said John Lewis and
OL,13,FWaitrose partners would receive an
OL,14,Finflation-busting 6.9% pay increase as
OL,15,Fpart of a #108 million investment in
OL,16,Fits workforce.
OL,18,FOn Thursday, the company will also
OL,19,Fshed more light on the progress of its
OL,20,Fmajor transformation under chair Jason
OL,21,FTarry.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
