CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773052871
OL,3,CWill John Lewis pay staff an annual
OL,4,Cbonus for first time in four years?
OL,6,FThe company's strategy under the
OL,7,Fformer Tesco UK boss has seen it pump
OL,8,Fmore investment into its stores as JLP
OL,9,Frenewed its focus in its core retail
OL,10,Fbusiness.
OL,12,FThe firm is currently investing #800
OL,13,Fmillion across its stores as part of a
OL,14,Flong-term investment.
OL,16,FIt has refurbished 23 Waitrose stores
OL,17,Fover the past year, as well as five
OL,18,FJohn Lewis shops.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
