OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773052871
OL,3,CWill John Lewis pay staff an annual
OL,4,Cbonus for first time in four years?
OL,6,FIt also launched the Topshop brand
OL,7,Facross all its 32 department stores
OL,8,Flast month as part of investment into
OL,9,Fits fashion offer.
OL,11,FLast month, Mr Tarry also pulled the
OL,12,Fplug on the partnership's plans to
OL,13,Fbuild around 10,000 rental properties
OL,14,Fin order to focus further on retail.
OL,16,FIt abandoned the build-to-rent
OL,17,Fambitions launched under previous
OL,18,Fchairwoman Dame Sharon White in 2020,
OL,19,Fblaming higher costs and caution in
OL,20,Fthe property market.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/7
